{"tid":978360,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有隻白鴿企係街燈上柯屎 我中撚晒","createTime":"2019-01-12T00:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T17:23:07.000Z","uid":216800,"like":220,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"94f6ec2bb8e3e19aeee7ba7c0f43bc6c481be851","tid":978360,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:16:55.000Z","msg":"今朝早左半個鐘戰勝左張床<br />\n諗住舒舒服服沖個熱水涼慶祝今日如此強大既我再出門返工<br />\n點知去到小巴站排隊果時<br />\n聽到啪一聲 我feel到有水點彈左落我頸度<br />\n我仲手一摸 白色既？ 我深知不妙 即刻抬頭一望<br />\n有兩隻白鴿企係街燈上 即刻飛走咗<br />\n我屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚我要食乳鴿報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事後除低件外套行返屋企用花灑開到最熱噴走晒啲屎佢<br />\n 再消毒埋條頸 換埋件衫 再出門返工<br />\n又遲到<br />\n真係屌一聲 <br />\n以後同白鴿勢不兩立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8bc0195af353bab1c0548021ef04a8ca7b5054","tid":978360,"uid":178223,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:17:58.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"c714518d115a56401ab6b17a5c3b8fd61d7cca46","tid":978360,"uid":195944,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"啲衰雀會特登係你個頭上面飛過 一路飛一路痾 見過人俾雀屎擊中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲賤人一大早就會出去喂雀 引晒班傻鳩黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a70a1ace2a244ee23a0342f805753cc832a866e","tid":978360,"uid":78683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"4eb2ce157c4f8f8df03fba483f91a1fc52b1af80","tid":978360,"uid":36238,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T00:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100816/photo/0816-00176-081b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.